&lt;p&gt;The club&#039;s playing season is from April until the end of September each year.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The club welcomes new members. As well as full playing members, the club has a number of associate members who can enjoy the facilities of the clubhouse if they do not want to play bowls.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The annual membership fees will be set at the Annual General Meeting in February 2017. As a general guide, the fees in 20q6 were as below.&lt;/p&gt;

